CustomField.formula:
/* This field comes with the unmanaged package "Unsubscribe Link" from the AppExchange.*/
/* INSTRUCTIONS: For this formula to work, you need to create a record for the custom metadata type Unsubscribe Link */
/* Fill in the field SiteDomain with the domain of your Salesforce Site used for this purpose. */
/* You can optionally fill in the field Our Organization which will replace "our organization" in the formula results with the name of your org. */
/*What the formula is doing:*//* Create a hyperlink of SiteDomain from the custom metadata record*/

HYPERLINK(("https://"+$CustomMetadata.Unsubscribe_Link__mdt.Unsubscribe.Site_Domain__c

/* append the visualforce page "Unsubscribe" and the recordId of this record and the email address.*/
/* the unsubscribe link flow uses these variables to find the right records.*/

+"/Unsubscribe?recordId="+ CASESAFEID(Id) +"&Email=" +

/*some email addresses have plus signs in them, which need to be substituted for %2B to work in links.*/

(SUBSTITUTE(Email,"+","%2B"))), "Click here to unsubscribe from all email from " +

/* Look up the custom metadata type record to find a replacement for "our organization" if it exists.*/

(IF(ISBLANK($CustomMetadata.Unsubscribe_Link__mdt.Unsubscribe.Our_Organization__c),"our organization",$CustomMetadata.Unsubscribe_Link__mdt.Unsubscribe.Our_Organization__c) + "."))
